==1AC – plan text==&#xD;
&#xD;
The United States Environmental Protection Agency should exempt modified and new coal-fired power plants from Utility Mercury and Air Toxics Standards.  The Agency should change the carbon dioxide limit of the New Source Performance Standards for Greenhouse Gas Emissions for modified and new coal-fired power plants to 2,000 pounds per MWh.&#xD;
&#xD;
&#xD;
